 are concerned - basic computer, programming and probability theory background is required.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The course site contains links to the lecture videos, reading material and assignments.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-29T17:45:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"homematic-community/awesome-homematic","categoryHTML":"<h2>CCU Addons</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/thkl/hap-homematic\">HAP-HomeMatic</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/thkl/hap-homematic\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">183</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":183,\"repo\":\"thkl/hap-homematic\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - RaspberryMatic / CCU3 addon to access your HomeMatic devices from HomeKit. Its much like <a href=\"https://github.com/thkl/homebridge-homematic\">https://github.com/thkl/homebridge-homematic</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/thkl/homebridge-homematic\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">173</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCo